The Liposome Co Inc said it andits wholly-owned subsidiary, Liposome Japan Co Ltd, willsponsor a major seminar on liposome at Tokyo University onMarch  12, 1987.    Liposomes are microscopic man-made spheres, composed oflipids, that can be engineered to entrap drugs or otherbiologically active molecules within the lipid membranes of thespheres or in the aqueous space between the membranes, thecompany explained.    Leading academic, research and government institutions inJapan are expected to attend, the company said. Reuter&#3;